  <li>Create your OWN javascript code that contains a variable called &quot;fname&quot; and another called &quot;lname&quot;. Ask the user to enter fname and lname.  If the fname is 'John' and lname is 'Doe', display an alert message saying "Congratulations John, you just won a million dollars!"
